{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"repeatCount","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/repeatCount","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考</a></p>\n<p>这个属性表示动画将发生的次数。</p>\n<p>这个属性的值指定了重复的次数。它也可以包括用分数值表示。它的值必须大于 0。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法解释","title":"用法解释","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>类别</th>\n      <th>动画时间属性</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Value</td>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/SVG/Content_type#number\">&lt;number&gt;</a> | \"indefinite\"</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Animatable</td>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table><dl>\n  <dt id=\"number_2\">&lt;number&gt;</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Real numbers are specified in one of two ways. When used in a stylesheet, a &lt;number&gt; is defined as follows:</p>\n    <pre class=\"notranslate\">number ::= integer\n            | [+-]? [0-9]* \".\" [0-9]+\n</pre>\n    <p>This syntax is the same as the definition in CSS (CSS2, section 4.3.1).</p>\n    <p>When used in an SVG attribute, a &lt;number&gt; is defined differently, to allow numbers with large magnitudes to be specified more concisely:</p>\n    <pre class=\"notranslate\">number ::= integer ([Ee] integer)?\n            | [+-]? [0-9]* \".\" [0-9]+ ([Ee] integer)?\n</pre>\n    <p>Within the SVG DOM, a &lt;number&gt; is represented as a float, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGNumber\"><code>SVGNumber</code></a> or a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedNumber\"><code>SVGAnimatedNumber</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The following elements can use the <code>repeatCount</code> attribute</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#animation\">Animation elements</a> »</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[],"query":"svg.elements.animate.repeatCount"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法解释","id":"用法解释"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Elements","id":"elements"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"repeatCount","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"repeatCount","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/repeatcount","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/repeatcount/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG：可缩放矢量图形"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/repeatCount","title":"repeatCount"}],"pageTitle":"repeatCount - SVG：可缩放矢量图形 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}